title.en: Usotsuki Ookami wa Nido Propose Suru

description.en: When I entered college, a senpai helped me when I got lost. I, who have never known love, I got carried away by its beauty. But it was so popular that he was called "The Emperor of the high school" ... It 's impossible that it can become my ... I spent all the time to avoid him until he left school ... But a year later, is came back to find me ...
